msgstr "The hotspot needs to be manually configured and enabled."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:47
#: 53289d4b12bb41d1a99aa1915d21fbef
msgid "请问Combo-AT固件中 “AT+MQTTPUBRAW” 指令一次性最多可以发送多长的数据？"
msgstr ""
"In Combo-AT firmware, what is the maximum data length that can be sent at "
"one time using the \"AT+MQTTPUBRAW\" command?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:48
#: 322644fade1e4372b0f3f702e9b733e7
msgid "最多支持发送的数据长度为1024Bytes。"
msgstr "The maximum supported data length is 1024 Bytes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:51
#: 1c0168489b5a474a89bff6add97f6f7c
msgid ""
"请问博流1823号固件中 “ AT+MQTTPUBRAW ” 指令一次性最多可以发送多长的数据？"
msgstr ""
"In Bouffalo Lab firmware No. 1823, what is the maximum data length that can "
"be sent at one time using the \"AT+MQTTPUBRAW\" command?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:52
#: 7d5326c9150a42d5ba83022be47a42e6
msgid ""
"可发送的数据长度没有限制，由模组剩余内存大小决定，可通过指令“AT+SYSRAM”实时查"
"询模组剩余内存大小"
msgstr ""
"There is no fixed limit on the data length that can be sent. It depends on "
"the remaining memory size of the module. You can use the \"AT+SYSRAM\" "
"command to query the remaining memory size of the module in real time."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:55
#: a6117d14d0db4f19a01564cde9bdfebd
msgid "请问，Combo-AT固件订阅或者发布的主题长度有限制么，最长多少个字节？"
msgstr ""
"Is there a limit on the topic length for subscribing or publishing in Combo-"
"AT firmware? What is the maximum length in bytes?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:56
#: eec4966eeeeb42839db841694be65887
msgid "主题最长支持1008个字节；"
msgstr "The maximum supported topic length is 1008 bytes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:59
#: 320d55816fc94e1a8f10630177452c4a
msgid "请问Ai-WB2系列模组烧录用的是哪种接口，JTAG还是UART？"
msgstr ""
"Which interface is used to flash the Ai-WB2 series module, JTAG or UART?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:60
#: 6dec0c0c93d0452b9df40c8c3f8c961c
msgid "用的是串口烧录的方式；"
msgstr "It uses serial port flashing."

