#: 8921d40b7a814e3894391dcd34943142
msgid "请问用于wifi系列模组做TCP透传测试的网页有么？"
msgstr ""
"Is there a web page for TCP transparent transmission testing for Wi-Fi "
"series modules?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:64
#: e659aaf7dbf44d3a9cd6bfaf1a7d45c6
msgid "用这个链接：http://tt.ai-thinker.com:8000/ttcloud"
msgstr "Use this link: http://tt.ai-thinker.com:8000/ttcloud"

