msgid "请问WB2的wifi跟蓝牙功能的使用是否用的同一个串口？"
msgstr "Do the Wi-Fi and Bluetooth functions of WB2 use the same serial port?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:68
#: 236438fa04264b4cb983c89771320608
msgid "是的"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:71
#: 2e9137b110e34a5d99a6103fcb442768
msgid "WB2-32S写的最大连接数5个是什么意思"
msgstr "What does the maximum connection number of 5 written for WB2-32S mean?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:72
#: fd39644184d84e278b938fd99d19b31a
msgid "模块当热点使用的时候，可以接入5个设备"
msgstr ""
"When the module is used as a hotspot, up to 5 devices can connect to it."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:75
#: 3d52542d32ca4a1ea2304e5069b69423
msgid "请问有支ipv6的模组么？"
msgstr "Are there any modules that support IPv6?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:76
#: 9ba2f82bbeaa4bb88b00f122b9aee154
msgid ""
"目前没有出厂固件支持ipv6的模组，WB2系列模组支持ipv6，但是需要用户二次开发实"
"现；"
msgstr ""
"Currently, no module with factory firmware supports IPv6. The WB2 series "
"module supports IPv6, but users need to implement it through secondary "
"development."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:79
#: e2620ec121f9495692da1d88b5de34fc
msgid "WB2系列模组支持保持两个连接吗"
msgstr "Does the WB2 series module support maintaining two connections?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:80
#: 0a6070526405467f8bba964ecd968f66
msgid "支持保持两个连接，但不能同时收发数据"
msgstr ""
"It supports maintaining two connections, but cannot send and receive data "
"simultaneously."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:83
#: fdf0aab29bf04e339fb3d825319d8d13
msgid "请问：WB2系列模组的AP+STA是否可以同时并独立工作？"
msgstr ""
"Can the AP+STA mode of the WB2 series module work simultaneously and "
"independently?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:84
#: 3a22db4f779642e79b6c11c65de618ef
msgid "功能独立，时分复用。"
msgstr "The functions are independent and use time-division multiplexing."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:87
#: 56128f38f5944711b44159cb785a9a1d
msgid "WB2-32S模组，如何通过AT指令设置设备在路由器端的显示名称？"
msgstr ""
"For the WB2-32S module, how can I set the device display name on the router "
"side through AT commands?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:88
#: 0708ec6e766c498698bb7e1e714b516d
msgid "可以使用AT+CWHOSTNAME这个指令进行设置"
msgstr "You can use the AT+CWHOSTNAME command to set it."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:91
#: 7eb958c4056f49799448f8463bce61af
msgid "请问WB2-32S模组的固件有web配网功能么？"
msgstr ""
"Does the firmware of the WB2-32S module support web-based network "
"configuration?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:92
#: 3ee3ad9b2eb04a0cb451279a4f71b806
msgid "目前没有"
msgstr "Not currently."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:95
#: e6649434e4e84c3e9f5f0f85bec540a4
msgid "WB2模组连上路由之后如何访问互联网"
msgstr ""
"How can the WB2 module access the Internet after connecting to a router?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:96
#: 2785226f6bd4419c92323e264eaa72ec
msgid "通过TCP MQTT HTTP的方式"
msgstr "Through TCP, MQTT, or HTTP."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:99
#: 16b86df736fb40d1a8314d05b2de17c5
msgid "请问WB2作为AP实现配网的功能需要如何操作呢？"
msgstr ""
"How should WB2 be operated to implement network configuration as an AP?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:100
#: 0946d9a21a004ef883c7740a4ddbe610
msgid "作为AP配网功能需要用户自行设计，建议走TCP协议实现。"
msgstr ""
"The AP network configuration function needs to be designed by the user. It "
"is recommended to implement it through the TCP protocol."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:103
#: cb1319fb9dbd4999a38ed59bdd5e3c01
msgid "请问WB2作为AP可以手动配置加密模式么？"
msgstr "Can WB2 manually configure the encryption mode when used as an AP?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/wifi.rst:104
#: 892e41ab5a414e77b55e9bf7d86ec68b
msgid "可以的，但是需要烧录支持该功能的固件，若有需求，请联系安信可工作人员"
msgstr ""
"Yes, but firmware that supports this function needs to be flashed. If "
"needed, please contact Ai-Thinker staff."
